  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ixchel: Building understanding of the physical, cultural and socio-economic drivers of risk for strengthening resilience in the Guatemalan cordillera</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Informed by current socio-economic strategies and policies, this project aims to deliver improved knowledge, new datasets and cultural products, and build capacity to strengthen disaster risk reduction and response in multi-hazard environments. It aims to generate understanding about risk that is useful, usable and used to reduce the impact of future disasters in Guatemala, Latin America and globally.</narrative>
  </description>
